'''第56屆[[坎城影展|坎城影展]]'''於2003年5月14日至5月25日在[[法國|法國]][[坎城|坎城]]舉辦，開幕片為法國導演{{link-fr|傑哈·卡胡奇|Gérard Krawczyk}}執導的《{{link-fr|鬱金香方方|Fanfan la Tulipe (film, 2003)}}》，閉幕片則為美國導演{{link-en|理查·施克爾|Richard Schickel}}執導的《{{link-en|電影之光:卓別林的藝界人生|Charlie: The Life and Art of Charles Chaplin}}》。<ref name="a">{{cite news|url=http://www.urbancinefile.com.au/home/view.asp?a=7383&s=features|title=CANNES FILM FESTIVAL 2003 - PREVIEW|accessdate=10 December 2013|archive-date=2013-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214053022/http://www.urbancinefile.com.au/home/view.asp?a=7383&s=features|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本屆最高榮譽[[金棕櫚獎|金棕櫚獎]]頒給美國導演[[葛斯·范·桑|葛斯·范·桑]]執導的《[[大象_(電影)|大象]]》。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/2937274.stm|title=Cannes winners in full|accessdate=10 December 2013|work=BBC News|date=25 May 2003|archive-date=2013-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214162020/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/2937274.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2003/may/26/cannes2003.cannesfilmfestival|title=A disappointing Cannes finishes with controversial decisions|accessdate=10 December 2013|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304130502/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2003/may/26/cannes2003.cannesfilmfestival|dead-url=no}}</ref>

